{"tid":1056483,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"咩叫空難？曼聯話比你知咩叫空難","createTime":"2019-03-11T08:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T13:53:19.000Z","uid":5655,"like":3,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4da1c0ffab6633529e007eae977f6d6ab25fbe69","tid":1056483,"uid":5655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T08:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/11/165000_19cf889f6471e109455e0805976d0f42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F11%2F165000_19cf889f6471e109455e0805976d0f42.png&h=0d76a543&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/11/165002_0703081ed4cb6e9a24efc0a2e0faf694.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F11%2F165002_0703081ed4cb6e9a24efc0a2e0faf694.png&h=282dd286&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/11/165003_74186a1ffb057e3f617eaa03c478fc71.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F11%2F165003_74186a1ffb057e3f617eaa03c478fc71.png&h=3cc13f7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1958年2月6日，曼聯在客場擊敗貝爾格萊德紅星隊、晉級歐聯前身的歐洲冠軍球會盃四強之後，球員乘搭飛機返回曼徹斯特。飛機途中在慕尼黑機場加油，重新起飛後卻在覆滿冰雪的跑道上失事，造成包括8名曼聯球員和3名球會職員在內，共23人死亡，當時球隊主帥畢士比（Matt Busby）也重傷入院。"},{"pid":"b881c0b00e7286c1bd83d93c4a9691d41801550f","tid":1056483,"uid":72404,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T08:53:05.000Z","msg":"假膠引戰都高質啲啊唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲特登改個咁嘅名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84d021a81333a8dc80362808b0ab1f0be5e4d4f","tid":1056483,"uid":171754,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T08:54:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a232212a8aa508c5ca949bbefccfd816c7461be5","tid":1056483,"uid":29006,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"